{"tid":1599201,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"二手樓價連跌5週","createTime":"2019-09-28T00:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T03:46:55.000Z","uid":275872,"like":32,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"a451a4d7ce77e5c2975f18e83b316546be8f3d49","tid":1599201,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T00:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XA3JpA6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXA3JpA6.jpg&h=0aa544e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港住宅樓價持續向下，有地產代理行二手樓價指數，按周再挫0.34%，已連跌五個星期，累跌3.04%，為今年最長跌浪。當中港島區樓價跌勢最急，藍籌屋苑鰂魚涌太古城及鴨脷洲海怡半島個別單位成交價，已重返二○一七年水平。<br />\n<br />\n反映主要二手屋苑價格走勢的中原城市領先指數，自八月中以來持續回落，最新報182.66點，創四月中後新低。至於大型屋苑、中小型及大型單位指數齊瀉五周，當中以大型屋苑跌約3.38%最多。"},{"pid":"65f8a1baaef8aa8bfe29d8e625594dd9184d9721","tid":1599201,"uid":100256,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T00:55:47.000Z","msg":"從歷史高位回落3%咁多？ 咁咪即係樓爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e822220496076ce029ccf88cc892469fca143e55","tid":1599201,"uid":271894,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T00:58:45.000Z","msg":"跌左30% 先再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e329d12a91c9abab612765ba20d5a8ac7f19363","tid":1599201,"uid":146621,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T14:30:06.000Z","msg":"邊撚度有跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e92cf12ecb47918f988262e4f01772a7ed444f","tid":1599201,"uid":152225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T01:42:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\